Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: I was thrilled to be back in the beautiful Commonwealth of Pennsylvania with thousands of proud, hardworking American Patriots—67 days from now, we are going to win Pennsylvania, we are going to defeat Comrade Kamala Harris, and we are going to win the White House!
